msgid "# Atlas 300I DUO / Atlas 200I Pro"
msgstr "# Atlas 300I DUO / Atlas 200I Pro"

msgid ""
"This tutorial covers vLLM deployment on Ascend 310P inference hardware, including\n"
"Atlas 300I DUO and Atlas 200I Pro acceleration modules."
msgstr ""
"本教程介绍在昇腾310P推理硬件上部署vLLM，包括\n"
"Atlas 300I DUO和Atlas 200I Pro加速模块。"

msgid "Atlas 300I DUO does not support `triton` or `triton-ascend`."
msgstr "Atlas 300I DUO不支持`triton`或`triton-ascend`。"

msgid "## Run vLLM on Atlas 300I DUO"
msgstr "## 在Atlas 300I DUO上运行vLLM"

msgid "### Install Notes"
msgstr "### 安装说明"

msgid ""
"If installing from source, `vllm` and `vllm-ascend` may automatically pull "
"in `triton` and `triton-ascend` dependencies, which may cause unexpected "
"issues on Atlas 300I DUO. Please uninstall them before running on Atlas 300I"
" DUO:"
msgstr ""
"如果从源码安装，`vllm`和`vllm-ascend`可能会自动引入`triton`和`triton-ascend`依赖，这在Atlas 300I "
"DUO上可能导致意外问题。请在Atlas 300I DUO上运行前卸载它们："

msgid "### Graph Mode Notes"
msgstr "### 图模式说明"

msgid ""
"The current release supports `FULL_DECODE_ONLY` graph mode on Atlas 300I DUO"
" devices, but the following limitations apply due to hardware event-id "
"resource constraints:"
msgstr "当前版本在Atlas 300I DUO设备上支持`FULL_DECODE_ONLY`图模式，但由于硬件事件ID资源限制，存在以下限制："

msgid ""
"- When multiple Tensor Parallel (TP) ranks are enabled, the number of capturable graphs is limited and depends on the model depth. For example, Qwen3-32B can capture and replay 2 graphs.\n"
"    - There is no such limitation when TP=1.\n"
"    - We have reached out to the relevant experts for a solution. A software-based fix is considered feasible, but full support will take additional time. Thank you for your understanding."
msgstr ""
"- 当启用多个张量并行（TP）等级时，可捕获的图数量受限，具体取决于模型深度。例如，Qwen3-32B可以捕获并重放2个图。\n"
"    - 当TP=1时，没有此限制。\n"
"    - 我们已联系相关专家寻求解决方案。基于软件的修复被认为是可行的，但完全支持需要额外时间。感谢您的理解。"

msgid "### Deployment"
msgstr "### 部署"

msgid "Choose the startup command according to your hardware form factor."
msgstr "根据您的硬件形态选择启动命令。"

msgid "#### Atlas 300I DUO"
msgstr "#### Atlas 300I DUO"

msgid "Run docker container:"
msgstr "运行Docker容器："

msgid "#### Atlas 200I Pro Acceleration Module"
msgstr "#### Atlas 200I Pro加速模块"

msgid ""
"When starting a container on Atlas 200I Pro, mount additional driver libraries and\n"
"configuration files required by `npu-smi`. Without these mounts, `npu-smi` commands\n"
"may fail inside the container. Use the command below for your container OS."
msgstr ""
"在Atlas 200I Pro上启动容器时，请挂载`npu-smi`所需的额外驱动库和\n"
"配置文件。如果没有这些挂载，容器内的`npu-smi`命令\n"
"可能会失败。请根据您的容器操作系统使用以下命令。"

msgid ""
"Atlas 200I Pro also uses Ascend 310P. Adjust `--device=/dev/davinci0` according to\n"
"    the NPU ID you want to use. You can query available devices with\n"
"    `ll /dev/ | grep davinci`."
msgstr ""
"Atlas 200I Pro也使用昇腾310P。请根据您要使用的NPU ID调整\n"
"    `--device=/dev/davinci0`。您可以通过\n"
"    `ll /dev/ | grep davinci`查询可用设备。"

