msgstr "=== \"Ubuntu 24.04\""

msgid "=== \"openEuler 24.03\""
msgstr "=== \"openEuler 24.03\""

msgid "Set up environment variables:"
msgstr "设置环境变量："

msgid "### Online Inference on NPU"
msgstr "### NPU上的在线推理"

msgid ""
"For Atlas 300I DUO (310P), do not rely on `max-model-len` auto detection\n"
"    (that is, do not omit the `--max-model-len` argument), because it may cause OOM."
msgstr ""
"对于Atlas 300I DUO（310P），不要依赖`max-model-len`自动检测\n"
"    （即不要省略`--max-model-len`参数），因为这可能导致OOM。"

msgid "Reason, based on the current 310P attention path:"
msgstr "原因，基于当前的310P注意力路径："

msgid ""
"- `AscendAttentionMetadataBuilder310` passes `model_config.max_model_len`\n"
"      to `AttentionMaskBuilder310`.\n"
"    - `AttentionMaskBuilder310` builds a full causal mask with shape\n"
"      `[max_model_len, max_model_len]` in float16, then converts it to FRACTAL_NZ.\n"
"    - In the 310P `attention_v1` prefill/chunked-prefill path\n"
"      (`_npu_flash_attention` / `_npu_paged_attention_splitfuse`),\n"
"      this explicit mask tensor is consumed directly, and there is currently\n"
"      no compressed-mask path."
msgstr ""
"- `AscendAttentionMetadataBuilder310`将`model_config.max_model_len`\n"
"      传递给`AttentionMaskBuilder310`。\n"
"    - `AttentionMaskBuilder310`构建一个形状为\n"
"      `[max_model_len, max_model_len]`的float16完整因果掩码，然后将其转换为FRACTAL_NZ。\n"
"    - 在310P `attention_v1`预填充/分块预填充路径\n"
"      (`_npu_flash_attention` / `_npu_paged_attention_splitfuse`)中，\n"
"      此显式掩码张量被直接消费，目前\n"
"      没有压缩掩码路径。"

msgid ""
"If auto detection resolves to a large context length, the mask allocation\n"
"    (`O(max_model_len^2)`) may exceed NPU memory and trigger OOM.\n"
"    Always set an explicit and conservative value, for example `--max-model-len 16384`."
msgstr ""
"如果自动检测解析出较大的上下文长度，掩码分配\n"
"    (`O(max_model_len^2)`)可能会超出NPU内存并触发OOM。\n"
"    始终设置一个明确且保守的值，例如`--max-model-len 16384`。"

msgid ""
"Run the following commands to start the vLLM server on NPU for the Qwen3 "
"Dense series."
msgstr "运行以下命令，在NPU上为Qwen3 Dense系列启动vLLM服务器。"

msgid "#### Prepare Model Weights"
msgstr "#### 准备模型权重"

msgid ""
"Use the W8A8SC quantized weights from the Eco-Tech official ModelScope "
"repository."
msgstr "使用来自Eco-Tech官方ModelScope仓库的W8A8SC量化权重。"

msgid ""
"Once the server is started, you can query the model with input prompts:"
msgstr "服务器启动后，您可以使用输入提示查询模型："

msgid "### Offline Inference"
msgstr "### 离线推理"

msgid ""
"Run the following script, `example.py`, to execute offline inference on NPU."
msgstr "运行以下脚本`example.py`，在NPU上执行离线推理。"

msgid "Run script:"
msgstr "运行脚本："

msgid "If the script runs successfully, you can see the generated result."
msgstr "如果脚本运行成功，您可以看到生成的结果。"

msgid "### Closing Notes"
msgstr "### 结束语"

msgid ""
"For early access to Qwen3-MoE, Qwen3-VL, and preview support for Qwen3.5 and"
" Qwen3.6 with performance acceleration, follow #7394 for updated deployment "
"guidance."
msgstr ""
"如需抢先体验Qwen3-MoE、Qwen3-VL，以及Qwen3.5和Qwen3.6的性能加速预览支持，请关注#7394以获取更新的部署指南。"

